Animation by Eric DeFreitas
In the last three years, Canadian Master Sommelier Jennifer Huether has noticed consumer interest in vegan wines rapidly increase. As a result, the number of winemakers now racing to certify their products as vegan-friendly &ldquo;has literally exploded,&rdquo; she says, calling it &ldquo;a massive shift.&rdquo;
